subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Chez Reavie, a 26-year-old PGA Tour rookie, finished the rain-delayed first round of the Canadian Open in Oakville, Ontario, with a six-under-par 65. He then shot 64 in the second round to take a two-stroke lead over Eric Axley, who was 11 under with a hole remaining when play was suspended because of darkness.
